      "line": 45,
      "message": "so we don't need this?\n\n  private List<@NotNull @Valid ConfigurationEntity> configurationEntities;\n\nI'm not sure that this will cause validation of the values contained within the list:\n\n  @Valid private List<XXX> yyy;",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 811,
        "name": "Jim Hahn",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jrh3@att.com",
